data.description: WELCOME HOME!! This unique tri-level floor plan has room for everyone!  4 Bedrooms and 3 full baths and a large great room with vaulted ceilings and a gas fireplace.  The kitchen has a breakfast bar, an eat in nook at the bay windows with French doors opening to the dual covered patios.  The bathrooms have updated showers and a separate tub in the primary bathroom.  All rooms have ceiling fans with lights, blinds throughout, and generously sized closets.  The downstairs boasts two bedrooms (one with a full wall of built in cabinets) a full bath, laundry closet and a large closet under the stairs for extra storage.  This home also has a three car garage with lots of cabinets and storage.  Very close to River Mountain Park, the dog park and the 35 mile trail loop.  Don't miss this one!!
